name: Airdrie Airshow 2013: Lockheed L-188 Electra Water Bomber (HD)
description:
Hey everyone, this is Part 2 in a 3 part series of videos from the 2013 Airdrie Regional Airshow. Part 2 features a Lockheed L-188 Electra Water Bomber taking off, dropping some water for the spectators, and then landing. This was pretty exciting for me as well, because I've never seen a Lockheed Electra before.

Thanks for watching, I hope you enjoyed the video. Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
